# Step 5: Install NGINX Gateway Fabric

Install:

```bash id="lab618"
helm install nginx-gateway \
oci://ghcr.io/nginxinc/charts/nginx-gateway-fabric \
--version 1.2.0 \
--create-namespace \
-n nginx-gateway
```

Verify:

```bash id="lab619"
kubectl get pods -n nginx-gateway
```

