# Step 8: Deploy Applications

## red.yaml

```yaml id="lab627"
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: red

spec:
  replicas: 2

  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: red

  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: red

    spec:
      containers:
      - name: red
        image: hashicorp/http-echo:0.2.3

        args:
        - "-text=Hello from RED Deployment"
        - "-listen=:80"

        ports:
        - containerPort: 80

---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: red-service

spec:
  selector:
    app: red

  ports:
  - port: 80
    targetPort: 80
```

Apply:

```bash id="lab628"
kubectl apply -f red.yaml
```

